Plain-English Summary

Phase 3 is the line between thinking and doing. Reading and discussion are free. Building, testing, deploying, or using this architecture in any funded or operational context requires a paid execution license. The license exists to replace months of internal architectural churn with a clear, bounded permission to move forward.
